The visual specification editor is an original ctsemgui integration using
Cytoscape.js and cytoscape-edgehandles (MIT; see bundled license files).

The product concept and selected interaction patterns were informed by
lavaangui by Julian D. Karch, licensed GPL-3.0-or-later:
https://github.com/karchjd/lavaangui

This editor does not embed lavaangui or depend on lavaan.
